translation.Name: Greece Note Deployment
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Looks like I'm being deployed to F.O.B. Heracles in the Keres Zone tomorrow, I can't decide if I'm excited or terrified.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: I'll get to see these "zombies" firsthand, finally. I've heard the stories and seen the damage, but surely they can't be as horrifying as everyone has said.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: I hear the gunfire all night, afterall, it is literally just over the mountain. Are there really that many? I guess these questions will be answered tomorrow...
